Organization Name: DUBLIN HOUSING AUTHORITY | ADMINISTRATION | PUBLIC AND MULTI-FAMILY HOUSING
Description: Provides public housing and section 8 properties.

Organization Name: GRANDVIEW HOUSING AUTHORITY | MAIN OFFICE | HOUSING AUTHORITY
Description: Provides public housing services to residents of City of Grandview. Operating 20 affordable units across its public housing.

Organization Name: HOUSING AUTHORITY CITY OF BRIDGEPORT | MAIN OFFICE | HOUSING AUTHORITY
Description: Administers low-income public housing with water paid. Waiting list varies depending on the size of the property needed.

Organization Name: HOUSING AUTHORITY CITY OF CLEBURNE | MAIN OFFICE | SUBSIDIZED HOUSING
Description: Administers the Housing Choice Voucher Program (Section 8) for the City of Cleburne to low-income, elderly and disabled families. Participants must locate their own rental unit that qualifies for the program.Applications open and close without notice. Referral to this agency does not guarantee applications are being accepted.

Organization Name: HOUSING AUTHORITY OF THE CITY OF DECATUR | MAIN OFFICE | LOW INCOME HOUSING
Description: Provides low income housing through 28 public housing units duplexes.Note: This organization does not participate in the Section 8 Housing Choice Voucher program, so voucher holders cannot participate in this housing authority; Does not offer emergency housing. *** Waitlist is 1 to 2 years for housing.Referral to this agency does not guarantee applications are being accepted.

Organization Name: HOUSING AUTHORITY OF THE CITY OF GRANBURY | MAIN OFFICE | HOUSING AUTHORITY
Description: Provides low income public housing for families, elderly, and disabled.

Organization Name: HOUSING AUTHORITY OF THE CITY OF HALTOM CITY | MAIN OFFICE | SENIOR HOUSING
Description: Administers one low income housing project subsidized by HUD. There is a total of 150 apartments located on this one site with 80 units designated for Older Adults citizens age 62 and older, the remainder are for families. This housing authority is a smoke-free environment.Note: This is NOT a Section 8 Program. Applications open and close without notice. Referral to this agency does not guarantee applications are being accepted.

Organization Name: MINERAL WELLS HOUSING AUTHORITY | MAIN OFFICE | SUBSIDIZED HOUSING
Description: Administers Section 8 vouchers and a low income rental housing program.Applications open and close without notice. Referral to this agency does not guarantee applications are being accepted.

Organization Name: WEATHERFORD HOUSING AUTHORITY | WEATHERFORD OFFICE | HOUSING AUTHORITY
Description: Provides Section 8 rental assistance to residents of Parker County. No emergency housing provided.
